data.description: OPEN SUN, 12/17, 2-4pm - WOW!  Even better value!  $10K price drop makes this the best value in Burke!  Gorgeous, renovated, and updated townhome in the heart of Burke!  Tucked away in the quiet enclave of homes on Spring Oak Ct., this lovely home is model-perfect and move in ready.   MOVE QUICK on this fabulous 3 BR, 1.5 BA townhome updated top to bottom!  Fully remodeled kitchen, fully remodeled full bath and half-bath, upgraded lighting, with large, light-filled bedrooms, and multiple walk-in closets and storage throughout!  Spacious family room with corner fireplace welcomes you to this charming  home.  Hand-scraped hardwood flooring throughout main level.  Chef's kitchen with loads of premium cabinetry, stainless appliances,  granite counters and custom built coffee bar!  Large kitchen overlooks adjacent dining area with double doors overlooking private patio and backyard. Enjoy your outdoor coffee or evening dinner on your private, fully-fenced patio surrounded by trees.   Built-in desk with additional shelving on main level,  custom shelving with hand-made barn doors,  and pull-down attic stairs for loads of additional storage!  One dedicated parking space with ample visitor parking throughout.  This lovely home is tucked away in the neighborhood for the utmost in privacy, tranquility, and space!   Easy walking distance to Burke Centre Shopping Center (Kohls, Chick Fil A, Safeway and so much more!).  And (almost) in your backyard is  Lake Barton -  Enjoy a walk after dinner on the beautiful walking trails overlooking the water!  A commuter's dream location!  Burke Centre offers multiple Metro bus stops, buses direct to Pentagon, VRE within minutes, and Springfield Metro just minutes away.  Just moments from Rt. 123 and the Fairfax County Parkway, within 10 minutes to the Beltway, downtown Fairfax, George Mason University, and more!  Enjoy nearby trails and parks throughout Burke Centre, as well as pools, tennis,  and other  amenities throughout this lovely community.    Burke Lake Park, with golf, train, ice-cream shop, and more...are just minutes away, as is the quaint village of Occoquan, and historic arts center at Lorton's Workhouse.   School pyramid of Bonnie Brae and Robinson Secondary!  This home offers the best of all worlds - a lovely move-in ready upgraded home, an amenity rich community, and a perfect commuter location in the heart of Burke!  OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY, 12/10, 1-4pm!
